  "description": "<p style=\"margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px\">We create limited edition hand made skateboards. Each are made&nbsp;from rare and exotic materials from an old lumber yard with no name that is equally as weird as our mill.&nbsp;We pick out as much crazy wood as we strap to our&nbsp;bikes and ride back to the mill. Each deck is made uniquely based on however Simon is feeling that day, so each one is completely unique of course.</p><p>These little guys take some time to make because it is all done by hand.&nbsp;Everything is cut, shaped, and finished using rusty tools and four pairs of average eyes. There is no big machine named \"Betsy\" that bashes out skateboards - just some time and hard work to chase down our youth.</p><p>We are totally about creating something beautiful and fun. For a few minutes you a can fly freely with a warm sun and a smile on your face.</p><p> </p><p> </p>",
